dct_title_s: Regni Hispaniae post omium editiones locupletissima descriptio
dct_description_sm: Johann bussemecher exc. ; Henricus Nagel fecit.
Shows political boundaries, topography, vegetation, waterways.
Dedication across top: Solis ad occasum regi subjecta Phillipo ...
Appears in Quad's Europae totius orbis terrarum partis praestantissimae, universalis et particularis descriptio, Cologne, 1600.
